import sys
import threading

def main():
    input = sys.stdin.readline
    t = int(input())

        if n % 2 == 0:
            print(-1)
        else:
            res = []
            for i in range(1, n+1, 2):
                res.append(i)
            for i in range(n-1, 1, -2):

            print(*res)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    threading.Thread(target=main).start()
